# Input: schema.cedarschema
```cedar
// Email-Based Domain Access Control — access decisions based on email
// domain and local-part patterns. Exercises Cedar's `like` glob
// operator (the only string-matching primitive in base Cedar).

entity User = {
    email: String,
};

entity Resource = {
    classification: String,  // "public" | "internal" | "partner"
};

action readResource, writeResource appliesTo {
    principal: [User],
    resource: [Resource],
};
```
